806
01:22:39.543 --> 01:22:41.779
Lew./
Ya?

807
01:22:43.480 --> 01:22:44.947
Kita harus bicara.

808
01:22:44.949 --> 01:22:46.084
Kolonel.

809
01:22:48.852 --> 01:22:51.123
Sebentar saja.

810
01:22:56.061 --> 01:22:57.594
Jenderal./
Apa kabar?

811
01:22:57.596 --> 01:22:59.194
Baik, baik.
Kabarmu?

